value: SE Colombia to ne Peru and w Amazonian Brazil

Southeastern Colombia in Comisaria de Caqueta (Florencia; Morelia) and Intendencia de Amazonas (Loretoyacu); eastern Ecuador; northeast- ern Peru in Department of Loreto south to the lower Huallaga and the upper Ucayali; western Brazil on the Rio lea and the upper Jurua.
